# chmod 640 numeric.txt
# ls -l numeric.txt

Assign 440:

# chmod 440 numeric.txt
# ls -l numeric.txt

Assign 600:

# chmod 600 numeric.txt
# ls -l numeric.txt

--------------------------------------------------
Exercise 7: Symbolic Permission Method
--------------------------------------------------

Create a file:

# touch symbolic.txt

Assign permissions:

# chmod u=rwx,g=rw,o=r symbolic.txt

Verify:

# ls -l symbolic.txt

Expected Permission:

-rwxrw-r--

--------------------------------------------------
Exercise 8: Modify Existing Permissions
--------------------------------------------------

Remove execute permission from user:

# chmod u-x symbolic.txt

Remove read and write from group:

# chmod g-rw symbolic.txt

Add read permission for others:

# chmod o+r symbolic.txt

Verify:

# ls -l symbolic.txt

