--------------------------------------------------
Exercise 11: Verify Default Permissions
--------------------------------------------------

Create file and directory:

# touch testfile
# mkdir testdir

Verify:

# ls -ld testfile testdir

Expected Permissions:

-rw-r--r-- testfile
drwxr-xr-x testdir

Calculation:
------------

File:
666
022
---
644

Directory:
777
022
---
755

