--------------------------------------------------

Set umask:

# umask 222

Verify:

# umask

Create file and directory:

# touch tempfile
# mkdir tempdir

Check permissions:

# ls -ld tempfile tempdir

Calculation:
------------

File:
666
222
---
444

Directory:
777
222
---
555

Expected:

-r--r--r--
dr-xr-xr-x

--------------------------------------------------
Exercise 13: Restore Default Umask
--------------------------------------------------

# umask 022

Verify:

# umask

--------------------------------------------------
Exercise 14: Set Permanent Umask
--------------------------------------------------

Open .bash_profile:

# vi ~/.bash_profile

Add the following line:

umask 222

Save and Exit.

Apply changes:

# source ~/.bash_profile

Verify:

# umask

