Exercise 15: Permission Troubleshooting
--------------------------------------------------

Create a file:

# touch secure.txt

Remove all permissions:

# chmod 000 secure.txt

Verify:

# ls -l secure.txt

Try to read:

# cat secure.txt

Observe:
---------
Permission denied

Restore permission:

# chmod 644 secure.txt

